room_title: Escape room "Ozark Mafia" by Escape Plan in Columbia (MO)
room_description: At one point, Jimmy Smallfingers was one of the top money launderers for the Ozark Mafia. But Jimmy went rogue stealing $1,000,000 and the ringleader’s most prized gun. Now the Kingpin has made it your job to get back what is his. You think you’ve found Jimmy’s hideout and the boss says you have 60 minutes... come back with everything that was taken, or don’t come back at all.
